<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>MatchApply — Encontrá el trabajo indicado</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bricolage+Grotesque:opsz,wght@12..96,600;12..96,700;12..96,800&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pdf.js/3.11.174/pdf.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mammoth/1.6.0/mammoth.browser.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg:#fbfbfd; --surface:#fff; --panel:#f5f5f7; --ink:#1d1d1f; --ink-2:#6e6e73; --ink-3:#86868b;
    --blue:#0071e3; --blue-hover:#0077ed; --border:#d2d2d7; --border-2:#e8e8ed;
    --green:#1d8a4e; --green-soft:#e7f4ec; --amber:#9a6a00; --amber-soft:#f6efdd; --red:#c0362c; --red-soft:#f7e6e4;
    --navy:#15294d;
    --shadow-sm:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06),0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
    --shadow-md:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08); --shadow-lg:0 20px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.16);
  }
  * { box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
  html { -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; text-rendering:optimizeLegibility; scroll-behavior:smooth; }
  body { color:var(--ink); background:var(--bg); min-height:100vh; line-height:1.47;
    font-family:'Manrope',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; letter-spacing:-0.01em; }
  ::selection { background:#b3d7ff; }
  .wrap { max-width:1000px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 22px; }
  .narrow { max-width:720px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 22px; }

  nav.top { position:sticky; top:0; z-index:100; height:48px; background:rgba(251,251,253,.8);
    backdrop-filter:saturate(1.8) blur(20px); -webkit-backdrop-filter:saturate(1.8) blur(20px); border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
  .nav-inner { max-width:1000px; margin:0 auto; height:100%; padding:0 22px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; }
  .nav-logo { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; cursor:pointer; }
  .nav-logo .mark { width:26px; height:26px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }
  .nav-logo .mark svg, .hero-logo svg { width:100%; height:100%; display:block; }
  .nav-logo strong { font-size:16px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.02em; }
  .nav-right { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; }
  .nav-links { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; }
  .nav-links button { background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; font-size:13px; font-weight:400;
    color:var(--ink-2); padding:6px 12px; border-radius:8px; transition:color .15s; letter-spacing:-0.01em; }
  .nav-links button:hover { color:var(--ink); }
  .nav-links button.active { color:var(--ink); font-weight:500; }
  .nav-cta { background:var(--blue) !important; color:#fff !important; border-radius:980px !important; padding:6px 15px !important; font-weight:500 !important; }
  .nav-cta:hover { background:var(--blue-hover) !important; }
  .lang { position:relative; margin-left:4px; }
  .lang-btn { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:50%; border:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--panel); color:var(--ink-2); cursor:pointer; transition:transform .25s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), color .15s, background .15s; }
  .lang-btn:hover { transform:scale(1.12); color:var(--ink); background:var(--border-2); }
  .lang-menu { position:absolute; right:0; top:42px; background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:12px; box-shadow:var(--shadow-md); padding:6px; display:none; flex-direction:column; min-width:150px; z-index:130; }
  .lang-menu.open { display:flex; }
  .lang-menu button { background:none; border:none; text-align:left; font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-2); padding:9px 12px; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; transition:background .12s; }
  .lang-menu button:hover { background:var(--panel); color:var(--ink); }
  .lang-menu button.active { color:var(--blue); font-weight:600; }
  .disclaimer { display:flex; gap:9px; align-items:flex-start; background:var(--amber-soft); border:1px solid rgba(154,106,0,.25); border-radius:12px; padding:12px 14px; font-size:13px; color:#7a5500; line-height:1.5; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .disclaimer svg { flex-shrink:0; margin-top:1px; }
  /* nav iterativa */
  .nav-logo { transition:transform .25s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1); }
  .nav-logo:hover { transform:scale(1.05); }
  .nav-links button { transition:color .15s, background .15s, transform .22s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1); }
  .nav-links button:hover { transform:scale(1.06); }
  .nav-cta:hover { transform:scale(1.06); }
  /* account */
  .acct-btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:980px; padding:5px 12px 5px 7px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; font-size:13px; font-weight:500; color:var(--ink); transition:transform .22s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), background .15s; }
  .acct-btn:hover { transform:scale(1.05); background:var(--border-2); }
  .acct-av { width:23px; height:23px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--navy); color:#fff; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; }
  .plan-badge { font-size:10px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.04em; text-transform:uppercase; padding:2px 7px; border-radius:980px; }
  .plan-badge.free { background:var(--border-2); color:var(--ink-2); } .plan-badge.pro { background:linear-gradient(90deg,#0071e3,#7b2ff7); color:#fff; }
  .acct-menu { position:absolute; right:0; top:44px; background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:14px; box-shadow:var(--shadow-md); padding:8px; display:none; flex-direction:column; min-width:230px; z-index:130; }
  .acct-menu.open { display:flex; }
  .acct-menu .am-h { padding:8px 10px 10px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-2); margin-bottom:6px; }
  .acct-menu .am-h b { color:var(--ink); display:block; font-size:14px; } .acct-menu .am-h span { font-size:12.5px; color:var(--ink-3); }
  .acct-menu button.am-i { background:none; border:none; text-align:left; font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink); padding:9px 10px; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:9px; }
  .acct-menu button.am-i:hover { background:var(--panel); }
  .pro-btn { background:linear-gradient(90deg,#0071e3,#7b2ff7) !important; color:#fff !important; }
  .prolock { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; font-size:10.5px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.03em; color:#7b2ff7; background:rgba(123,47,247,.12); padding:2px 8px; border-radius:980px; }
  .credits { font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-2); display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; margin-bottom:16px; background:var(--panel); padding:7px 13px; border-radius:980px; }
  .credits b { color:var(--ink); }
  .pro-actions { display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:18px; }
  .act-btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; font-family:inherit; font-size:13.5px; font-weight:500; padding:10px 16px; border-radius:980px; border:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--surface); color:var(--ink); cursor:pointer; transition:transform .18s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), border-color .15s; }
  .act-btn:hover { transform:scale(1.04); border-color:var(--ink-3); }
  .up-hero { text-align:center; } .up-ic { width:54px; height:54px; border-radius:16px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0071e3,#7b2ff7); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin:0 auto 12px; }
  .up-price { font-size:15px; color:var(--ink-2); margin:0 0 18px; text-align:center; } .up-price b { color:var(--ink); font-size:24px; }
  .up-list { list-style:none; display:grid; gap:11px; margin:0 0 20px; } .up-list li { display:flex; gap:10px; font-size:14.5px; align-items:flex-start; } .up-list li svg { color:var(--green); flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px; }
  .up-note, .demo-note { font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-3); text-align:center; margin-top:12px; line-height:1.5; }
  .load-modal { text-align:center; padding:14px 4px; } .load-ring { width:54px; height:54px; margin:6px auto 18px; border:4px solid var(--border-2); border-top-color:var(--blue); border-radius:50%; animation:spin 1s linear infinite; }
  .load-text { font-size:16px; font-weight:600; min-height:24px; } .load-sub { font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-3); margin-top:6px; }
  .auth-tabs { display:flex; gap:6px; background:var(--panel); border-radius:980px; padding:4px; margin-bottom:18px; } .auth-tabs button { flex:1; border:none; background:none; padding:9px; border-radius:980px; font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:var(--ink-2); cursor:pointer; } .auth-tabs button.active { background:var(--surface); color:var(--ink); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
  .fld { margin-bottom:12px; } .fld label { display:block; font-size:12.5px; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink-2); margin-bottom:5px; } .fld input { width:100%; border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:10px; padding:11px 13px; font-family:inherit; font-size:14.5px; } .fld input:focus { outline:none; border-color:var(--blue); box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(0,113,227,.12); }
  .consent { display:flex; gap:9px; align-items:flex-start; font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-2); margin:6px 0 16px; cursor:pointer; line-height:1.4; } .consent input { margin-top:2px; width:16px; height:16px; accent-color:var(--blue); flex-shrink:0; }
  .hist-item { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px; padding:11px 2px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-2); font-size:14px; } .hist-item .hi-d { font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-3); } .hist-del { background:none; border:none; color:var(--red); cursor:pointer; font-size:13px; }
  @media (max-width:620px){ .nav-links button.plain { display:none; } }

  .btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:6px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit;
    font-size:16px; font-weight:500; padding:12px 24px; border-radius:980px; border:none; transition:background .18s,transform .1s,box-shadow .18s; letter-spacing:-0.01em; text-decoration:none; }
  .btn-blue { background:var(--blue); color:#fff; }
  .btn-blue:hover { background:var(--blue-hover); } .btn-blue:active { transform:scale(.98); }
  .btn-outline { background:transparent; color:var(--blue); border:1px solid var(--border); }
  .btn-outline:hover { background:rgba(0,113,227,.06); border-color:var(--blue); }
  .btn-link { background:none; color:var(--blue); font-size:16px; font-weight:500; cursor:pointer; border:none; font-family:inherit; padding:6px 4px; }
  .btn-link:hover { text-decoration:underline; }
  .btn-sm { font-size:14px; padding:9px 18px; }
  .btn:disabled { opacity:.55; cursor:not-allowed; box-shadow:none; }
  #page-inicio .btn, #page-nosotros .btn, #page-inicio .btn-link, #page-nosotros .btn-link { transition:transform .25s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), background .18s, box-shadow .18s; will-change:transform; }
  #page-inicio .btn:hover, #page-nosotros .btn:hover, #page-inicio .btn-link:hover, #page-nosotros .btn-link:hover { transform:scale(1.06); text-decoration:none; }
  #page-inicio .btn:active, #page-nosotros .btn:active { transform:scale(1.01); }

  .page { display:none; animation:pagein .5s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1); }
  .page.active { display:block; }
  @keyframes pagein { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px);} to{opacity:1;transform:none;} }

  .hero { text-align:center; padding:70px 22px 60px; }
  .hero-logo { width:78px; height:78px; margin:0 auto 22px; cursor:pointer; transition:transform .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), filter .3s; filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 20px rgba(21,41,77,.22)); }
  .hero-logo:hover { transform:scale(1.08); filter:drop-shadow(0 14px 32px rgba(21,41,77,.36)); }
  .hero .eyebrow { font-size:17px; font-weight:600; color:var(--blue); margin-bottom:12px; }
  .hero h1 { font-size:clamp(40px,7vw,76px); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1.06; max-width:16ch; margin:0 auto 20px; }
  .hero p.sub { font-size:clamp(18px,2.6vw,24px); color:var(--ink-2); font-weight:400; max-width:42ch; margin:0 auto 30px; line-height:1.4; }
  .hero-actions { display:flex; gap:10px; justify-content:center; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }

  .section-pad { padding:70px 0; }
  .section-title { text-align:center; font-size:clamp(30px,4.5vw,48px); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.02em; line-height:1.1; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .section-intro { text-align:center; font-size:clamp(17px,2.2vw,21px); color:var(--ink-2); max-width:48ch; margin:0 auto 44px; }
  .cards-3 { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:20px; }
  .feature { background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:22px; padding:30px 26px; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); transition:transform .25s,box-shadow .25s; }
  .feature:hover { transform:translateY(-4px); box-shadow:var(--shadow-md); }
  .feature .ic { width:46px; height:46px; border-radius:12px; background:var(--panel); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .feature h3 { font-size:21px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.02em; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .feature p { font-size:15.5px; color:var(--ink-2); line-height:1.5; }
  .cta-band { background:var(--panel); border-radius:28px; text-align:center; padding:60px 30px; }
  .cta-band h2 { font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,42px); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.02em; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .cta-band p { font-size:18px; color:var(--ink-2); margin-bottom:26px; }

  .about-hero { text-align:center; padding:80px 22px 30px; }
  .about-hero .eyebrow { font-size:15px; font-weight:600; color:var(--blue); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .about-hero h1 { font-size:clamp(34px,5.5vw,60px); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1.08; max-width:18ch; margin:0 auto; }
  .about-body { font-size:19px; color:var(--ink); line-height:1.65; }
  .about-body p { margin-bottom:22px; } .about-body p.lead { font-size:22px; }
  .about-quote { font-size:clamp(21px,3.2vw,30px); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.02em; line-height:1.34; text-align:center; margin:32px auto; max-width:24ch; color:var(--ink); }
  .about-quote .q { margin:0; }
  .about-quote .by { color:var(--ink-3); display:block; font-size:14px; font-weight:500; margin-top:14px; letter-spacing:0; }
  .values { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:18px; margin-top:20px; }
  .value { background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:18px; padding:24px; }
  .value h4 { font-size:17px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:6px; } .value p { font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink-2); line-height:1.5; }
  hr.soft { border:none; border-top:1px solid var(--border-2); margin:46px 0; }

  .tools-hero { text-align:center; padding:66px 22px 26px; }
  .tools-hero h1 { font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,52px); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.03em; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .tools-hero p { font-size:19px; color:var(--ink-2); max-width:44ch; margin:0 auto; }
  .seg-wrap { display:flex; justify-content:center; margin:30px 0 26px; }
  .seg { display:inline-flex; background:var(--panel); border-radius:980px; padding:4px; gap:2px; max-width:100%; overflow-x:auto; }
  .seg button { border:none; background:none; padding:9px 18px; border-radius:980px; font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:var(--ink-2); cursor:pointer; white-space:nowrap; transition:color .15s; }
  .seg button.active { background:var(--surface); color:var(--ink); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }

  .card { background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:20px; padding:24px; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
  .prof-box { margin-bottom:26px; }
  .label-row { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .icon-chip { width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:9px; background:var(--panel); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; }
  .eyebrow { font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink-3); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; }
  .prof-upload { margin-left:auto; }
  textarea { width:100%; border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:14px; padding:14px; font-family:inherit; font-size:15px; color:var(--ink);
    resize:vertical; min-height:96px; line-height:1.55; background:var(--surface); transition:border-color .15s,box-shadow .15s; letter-spacing:-0.01em; }
  textarea:focus { outline:none; border-color:var(--blue); box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(0,113,227,.12); }
  .cv-status { font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-2); margin-top:10px; display:none; align-items:center; gap:7px; }
  .cv-status.show { display:flex; }
  .cv-status.ok { color:var(--green); }
  .chips { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:7px; margin-top:13px; align-items:center; }
  .chips-label { font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink-3); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.03em; margin-right:2px; }
  .chip { font-size:13px; font-weight:500; color:var(--ink); background:var(--panel); padding:4px 11px; border-radius:8px; }

  .panel-head { margin-bottom:20px; }
  .panel-head h2 { font-size:26px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.02em; margin-bottom:5px; }
  .panel-head p { font-size:15.5px; color:var(--ink-2); max-width:62ch; }
  .row-between { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .stats { display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .stat-pill { display:inline-flex; align-items:baseline; gap:6px; background:var(--panel); padding:7px 14px; border-radius:980px; font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-2); }
  .stat-pill b { font-size:15px; color:var(--ink); font-weight:600; } .stat-pill b.g { color:var(--green); }
  .hidden { display:none !important; }
  .selrow { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:22px; }
  .selrow label { font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:var(--ink-2); }
  select.js { font-family:inherit; font-size:15px; font-weight:500; color:var(--ink); background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:10px 14px; cursor:pointer; }
  select.js:focus { outline:none; border-color:var(--blue); box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(0,113,227,.12); }

  .batchbar { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:14px; flex-wrap:wrap; background:var(--panel); border-radius:16px; padding:14px 18px; margin:16px 0; }
  .batchbar .bb-text { font-size:15.5px; font-weight:500; } .batchbar .bb-text b { color:var(--blue); }
  .batchbar .bb-actions { display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .link-btn { background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-2); }
  .link-btn:hover { color:var(--ink); text-decoration:underline; }

  .jobs { display:grid; gap:14px; }
  .job { position:relative; background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:18px; padding:22px; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
    transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s,border-color .2s; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr auto; gap:20px; align-items:start; animation:fade .4s both; }
  @keyframes fade { from{opacity:0;} to{opacity:1;} }
  .job:hover { transform:translateY(-2px); box-shadow:var(--shadow-md); }
  .job.top-match { border-color:var(--green); } .job.selected { border-color:var(--blue); box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(0,113,227,.12); }
  .top-flag { display:inline-block; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--green); background:var(--green-soft); padding:3px 11px; border-radius:980px; margin-bottom:9px; }
  .job-main { min-width:0; }
  .titlerow { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:3px; }
  .job h3 { font-size:19px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.02em; line-height:1.2; }
  .partner { font-size:12px; font-weight:500; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:980px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; }
  .company { font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink-2); margin-bottom:10px; }
  .meta { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px 18px; font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-2); margin-bottom:13px; }
  .meta span { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:5px; }
  .reasons { list-style:none; display:grid; gap:6px; margin-bottom:16px; max-width:60ch; }
  .reasons li { font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-2); display:flex; gap:8px; line-height:1.45; }
  .reasons li .dash { flex-shrink:0; margin-top:7px; width:5px; height:5px; border-radius:50%; }
  .ph { height:12px; border-radius:6px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--panel) 25%,var(--border-2) 37%,var(--panel) 63%); background-size:400% 100%; animation:shimmer 1.4s ease infinite; margin-bottom:8px; }
  @keyframes shimmer { 0%{background-position:100% 0;} 100%{background-position:-100% 0;} }
  .score-col { display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:8px; min-width:92px; }
  .ring-wrap { position:relative; width:82px; height:82px; } .ring-wrap svg { transform:rotate(-90deg); }
  .ring-bg { stroke:var(--border-2); } .ring-fg { stroke-linecap:round; transition:stroke-dashoffset 1s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1); }
  .ring-num { position:absolute; inset:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }
  .ring-num b { font-size:23px; font-weight:700; line-height:1; letter-spacing:-0.02em; }
  .ring-num small { font-size:9px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; color:var(--ink-3); margin-top:2px; }
  .score-tag { font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding:3px 11px; border-radius:980px; white-space:nowrap; }
  .score-empty { width:82px; height:82px; border-radius:50%; border:1.5px dashed var(--border); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:var(--ink-3); font-size:11px; text-align:center; padding:8px; }
  .job-actions { grid-column:1/-1; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:18px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
  .selbox { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-2); cursor:pointer; }
  .selbox input { width:17px; height:17px; accent-color:var(--blue); cursor:pointer; }

  .kw-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:14px; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .kw-box { background:var(--panel); border-radius:16px; padding:18px; }
  .kw-box h5 { font-size:13px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .kw-list { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:7px; }
  .kw { font-size:13px; font-weight:500; padding:5px 12px; border-radius:980px; }
  .kw.has { background:var(--green-soft); color:var(--green); } .kw.miss { background:var(--amber-soft); color:var(--amber); }
  .adapted { background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:16px; padding:22px; }
  .adapted .tape { display:inline-block; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--blue); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .adapted h5 { font-size:18px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:9px; } .adapted p { font-size:15.5px; line-height:1.65; }
  .adapted .ins { background:var(--green-soft); color:var(--green); font-weight:600; padding:1px 5px; border-radius:5px; }
  .base-note { font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-2); margin-top:16px; padding-top:14px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-2); }

  .reader-toggle { display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:22px; }
  .reader-btn { font-size:14px; font-weight:500; cursor:pointer; background:var(--surface); color:var(--ink-2); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:980px; padding:9px 17px; font-family:inherit; transition:all .2s ease-in-out; }
  .reader-btn:hover { border-color:var(--ink-3); transform:translateY(-1px); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
  .reader-btn.active { background:var(--ink); color:#fff; border-color:var(--ink); }

  /* --- disclaimers de IA --- */
  /* aviso de IA: caption discreto, no un cartel */
  .disclaimer.ai { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; width:auto; max-width:100%;
    background:rgba(154,106,0,.05); border:1px solid rgba(154,106,0,.16); border-radius:8px;
    padding:5px 10px; margin:0 0 16px; font-size:11.5px; line-height:1.45; color:#8a7040;
    transition:background-color .25s var(--ease), border-color .25s var(--ease), color .25s var(--ease); }
  .disclaimer.ai:hover { background:rgba(154,106,0,.09); border-color:rgba(154,106,0,.28); color:#7a5500; }
  .disclaimer.ai svg { width:12px; height:12px; opacity:.75; margin-top:0; flex-shrink:0; }
  /* microcopy introductorio de cada subseccion */
  .tool-lead { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; margin:0 0 14px; font-size:13.5px; font-weight:500;
    color:var(--blue); letter-spacing:-0.005em; }
  .tool-lead::before { content:""; width:3px; height:15px; border-radius:3px; background:var(--blue); opacity:.55; flex-shrink:0; }
  .bot-note { display:flex; gap:6px; align-items:flex-start; padding:8px 12px 10px; background:var(--bg);
    border-top:1px solid var(--border-2); font-size:11px; line-height:1.4; color:var(--ink-3); }
  .bot-note svg { flex-shrink:0; margin-top:1px; opacity:.7; }

  /* --- selector de evaluador: tarjetas interactivas --- */
  .reader-cards { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:12px; margin-bottom:20px; }
  .reader-card { position:relative; text-align:left; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit;
    background:var(--surface); border:1.5px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:16px; padding:16px 16px 15px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);
    transition:transform .25s var(--ease), box-shadow .25s var(--ease), border-color .25s var(--ease),
               background-color .25s var(--ease), opacity .25s var(--ease); }
  .reader-cards:hover .reader-card { opacity:.7; }
  .reader-cards:hover .reader-card:hover { opacity:1; }
  .reader-card:hover { transform:translateY(-3px) scale(1.02); border-color:var(--blue); box-shadow:var(--shadow-md); background:#f7fbff; }
  .reader-card.active { opacity:1; border-color:var(--blue); border-width:2px; background:#f2f8ff;
    box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(0,113,227,.14), var(--shadow-md); }
  .reader-card .rc-top { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:9px; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .reader-card .rc-ic { width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:9px; background:var(--panel); color:var(--ink-2);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; transition:all .25s var(--ease); }
  .reader-card.active .rc-ic { background:var(--blue); color:#fff; }
  .reader-card h5 { font-size:14.5px; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink); }
  .reader-card p { font-size:12.5px; color:var(--ink-2); line-height:1.45; }
  .reader-card .rc-dot { position:absolute; top:14px; right:14px; width:16px; height:16px; border-radius:50%;
    border:1.5px solid var(--border); transition:all .25s var(--ease); }
  .reader-card.active .rc-dot { border-color:var(--blue); background:var(--blue); box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 3px #fff; }
  @media (max-width:720px){ .reader-cards { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
  .sw-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:14px; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .sw-box { border-radius:16px; padding:20px; } .sw-box.str { background:var(--green-soft); } .sw-box.wea { background:var(--amber-soft); }
  .sw-box h5 { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:12px; } .sw-box.str h5 { color:var(--green); } .sw-box.wea h5 { color:var(--amber); }
  .sw-box ul { list-style:none; display:grid; gap:9px; } .sw-box li { font-size:14px; display:flex; gap:8px; line-height:1.45; } .sw-box li b { flex-shrink:0; }
  .format-tip { background:var(--panel); border-radius:16px; padding:20px 22px; margin-bottom:16px; }
  .format-tip h5 { font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--blue); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; margin-bottom:9px; }
  .format-tip p { font-size:15px; line-height:1.65; }
  .improved { background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:16px; padding:22px; }
  .improved .tape { display:inline-block; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--green); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .improved h5 { font-size:17px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:9px; } .improved p { font-size:15px; line-height:1.7; }
  .improved ul { margin:12px 0 0; padding-left:18px; } .improved li { font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-2); margin-bottom:6px; line-height:1.45; }
  .improved .cvsec { margin-top:14px; padding-top:14px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-2); }
  .improved .cvh { font-size:12px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.05em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-3); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .improved .cvbul { margin:0; padding-left:18px; } .improved .cvbul li { font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink); margin-bottom:8px; line-height:1.5; }
  .improved .cvchanges { margin-top:16px; background:var(--panel); border-radius:12px; padding:14px 16px; }
  .improved .cvchanges ul { margin:0; padding-left:18px; } .improved .cvchanges li { font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink-2); margin-bottom:6px; }

  .role-grid { display:grid; gap:14px; }
  .role-card { background:var(--panel); border-radius:16px; padding:22px; }
  .role-card h5 { font-size:17px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:13px; }
  .role-card ul { list-style:none; display:grid; gap:10px; }
  .role-card li { font-size:14.5px; display:flex; gap:11px; line-height:1.5; }
  .role-card li .b { flex-shrink:0; width:22px; height:22px; border-radius:7px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; margin-top:1px; }
  .b.val { background:var(--green-soft); color:var(--green); } .b.imp { background:var(--amber-soft); color:var(--amber); } .b.prep { background:rgba(0,113,227,.1); color:var(--blue); }
  .qbox { background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:12px; padding:12px 14px; font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink-2); }
  .qbox + .qbox { margin-top:8px; }
  .subhead { font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink-3); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; margin:18px 0 10px; }

  .overlay { position:fixed; inset:0; background:rgba(0,0,0,.4); backdrop-filter:blur(4px); z-index:200; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:16px; animation:ovf .2s ease; }
  @keyframes ovf { from{opacity:0;} to{opacity:1;} }
  .modal { width:100%; max-width:470px; background:var(--surface); border-radius:22px; padding:26px; box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg); animation:pop .28s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1) both; max-height:88vh; overflow-y:auto; }
  @keyframes pop { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px) scale(.98);} to{opacity:1;transform:none;} }
  .modal-head { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .modal h3 { font-size:20px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.02em; line-height:1.25; }
  .modal .m-kick { font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--blue); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; margin-bottom:3px; }
  .xbtn { background:var(--panel); border:none; border-radius:50%; cursor:pointer; color:var(--ink-2); width:32px; height:32px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; }
  .xbtn:hover { background:var(--border-2); }
  .modal-sub { font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-2); margin:10px 0 16px; }
  .fields { display:grid; gap:8px; margin-bottom:18px; }
  .field { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; border:1px solid var(--border-2); background:var(--panel); border-radius:12px; padding:11px 14px; font-size:14px; transition:background .3s,border-color .3s; }
  .field.filled { background:var(--green-soft); border-color:rgba(29,138,78,.3); }
  .field .fl { color:var(--ink-2); } .field .fv { font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-3); display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; text-align:right; }
  .field.filled .fv { color:var(--green); font-weight:500; }
  .modal-done { text-align:center; padding-top:4px; }
  .modal-done .tick { width:50px; height:50px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--green-soft); color:var(--green); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin:0 auto 14px; }
  .modal-done p { font-size:17px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:5px; }
  .modal-done span.note { font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-2); display:block; margin-bottom:18px; line-height:1.5; }
  .btn.block { width:100%; }
  .filling-note { font-size:14px; text-align:center; color:var(--ink-2); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:8px; }
  .spin { animation:spin 1s linear infinite; } @keyframes spin { to{transform:rotate(360deg);} }

  footer.foot { border-top:1px solid var(--border-2); margin-top:40px; padding:26px 0 60px; text-align:center; font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-3); line-height:1.7; }

  /* Chatbot */
  #botBtn { position:fixed; right:24px; bottom:24px; z-index:180; width:58px; height:58px; border-radius:50%; border:none; cursor:grab;
    background:var(--navy); color:#fff; box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; touch-action:none; transition:transform .12s; }
  #botBtn:hover { transform:scale(1.05); } #botBtn:active { cursor:grabbing; }
  #botBtn .dot { position:absolute; top:6px; right:6px; width:11px; height:11px; border-radius:50%; background:#34c759; border:2px solid var(--navy); }
  #botPanel { position:fixed; right:24px; bottom:92px; z-index:181; width:340px; max-width:calc(100vw - 32px); background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2);
    border-radius:20px; box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg); display:none; flex-direction:column; overflow:hidden; animation:pop .24s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1) both; }
  #botPanel.open { display:flex; transform-origin:bottom right; }
  /* entrada: sube desde el boton flotante */
  #botPanel.open:not(.closing) { animation:botIn .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1) both; }
  @keyframes botIn {
    from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px) scale(.94); }
    to   { opacity:1; transform:none; }
  }
  /* salida: baja hacia la esquina inferior derecha antes de desmontarse */
  #botPanel.closing {
    pointer-events:none;
    animation:botOut .3s ease-in-out both;
  }
  @keyframes botOut {
    0%   { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0) scale(1); }
    35%  { opacity:.85; transform:translateY(-3px) scale(1.01); }   /* mini rebote antes de irse */
    100% { opacity:0; transform:translateY(22px) scale(.92); }
  }
  #botPanel.closing .bot-msgs, #botPanel.closing .bot-sugg { opacity:.5; transition:opacity .22s ease-in-out; }
  #botBtn.pulled { animation:botBtnPull .34s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1); }
  @keyframes botBtnPull { 0%{transform:scale(1);} 45%{transform:scale(1.13);} 100%{transform:scale(1);} }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
    #botPanel.open:not(.closing), #botPanel.closing, #botBtn.pulled { animation:none !important; }
  }
  .bot-head { background:var(--navy); color:#fff; padding:14px 16px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
  .bot-head .ava { width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:50%; background:rgba(255,255,255,.15); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; }
  .bot-head b { font-size:15px; font-weight:600; } .bot-head small { display:block; font-size:11px; opacity:.8; font-weight:400; }
  .bot-head .bx { margin-left:auto; background:none; border:none; color:#fff; cursor:pointer; opacity:.85; }
  .bot-msgs { padding:14px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px; height:300px; overflow-y:auto; background:var(--bg); }
  .bmsg { max-width:82%; font-size:14px; line-height:1.45; padding:9px 13px; border-radius:14px; }
  .bmsg.bot { background:var(--surface); border:1px solid var(--border-2); align-self:flex-start; border-bottom-left-radius:5px; }
  .bmsg.me { background:var(--blue); color:#fff; align-self:flex-end; border-bottom-right-radius:5px; }
  .bot-sugg { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:6px; padding:0 14px 10px; background:var(--bg); }
  .bot-sugg button { font-family:inherit; font-size:12.5px; color:var(--blue); background:rgba(0,113,227,.08); border:1px solid rgba(0,113,227,.2); border-radius:980px; padding:5px 11px; cursor:pointer; }
  .bot-sugg button:hover { background:rgba(0,113,227,.14); }
  .bot-input { display:flex; gap:8px; padding:12px; border-top:1px solid var(--border-2); background:var(--surface); }
  .bot-input input { flex:1; border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:980px; padding:9px 14px; font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; }
  .bot-input input:focus { outline:none; border-color:var(--blue); }
  .bot-input button { border:none; background:var(--blue); color:#fff; width:38px; height:38px; border-radius:50%; cursor:pointer; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; }

  @media (max-width:720px){
    .cards-3 { grid-template-columns:1fr; } .values { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .kw-grid,.sw-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; } .job { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .score-col { flex-direction:row; align-items:center; gap:12px; }
    .about-hero { padding:52px 18px 16px; } .about-body { font-size:16.5px; } .about-body p.lead { font-size:18.5px; }
    .about-quote { font-size:20px; margin:24px auto; max-width:100%; } .section-pad { padding:44px 0; }
    .narrow { padding:0 20px; }
  }

  /* ============================================================
     v2 — Navbar dinamica, bandas de seccion, hover de foco,
     transiciones globales y hoja de CV ejecutiva (A4)
     ============================================================ */
  :root { --tint-1:#f8fafc; --tint-2:#f1f5f9; --tint-line:#e6ecf3; --ease:cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1); }

  /* (10) transiciones globales */
  a, button, select, input, textarea,
  .feature, .value, .card, .job, .kw, .chip, .seg button, .reader-btn, .act-btn,
  .lang-menu button, .acct-menu button, .role-card, .qbox, .sw-box, .format-tip, .stat-pill {
    transition: background-color .3s var(--ease), color .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease),
                transform .3s var(--ease), opacity .3s var(--ease), box-shadow .3s var(--ease);
  }
  .page, .bot-msgs, .cv-doc { transition:opacity .3s var(--ease); }
  body.lang-swap .page, body.lang-swap .bot-msgs { opacity:.5; }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){ *,*::before,*::after{ transition:none !important; animation:none !important; } }

  /* (4) navbar dinamica */
  nav.top { height:52px; background:rgba(251,251,253,.72);
    backdrop-filter:saturate(1.9) blur(22px); -webkit-backdrop-filter:saturate(1.9) blur(22px);
    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
    box-shadow:0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.55) inset, 0 2px 14px rgba(15,32,60,.04);
    transition:background-color .3s var(--ease), box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease); }
  nav.top.scrolled { background:rgba(251,251,253,.92); box-shadow:0 4px 22px rgba(15,32,60,.09); }
  /* navbar: se esconde al bajar, vuelve al subir */
  nav.top { transform:translateY(0); will-change:transform;
    transition:transform .35s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), background-color .3s var(--ease), box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease); }
  nav.top.nav-hidden { transform:translateY(-100%); }
  .nav-links { gap:6px; }
  .nav-links button.plain { position:relative; transform-origin:center center; will-change:transform;
    transition:transform .25s ease-in-out, color .25s ease-in-out, background-color .25s ease-in-out,
               font-weight .25s ease-in-out, letter-spacing .25s ease-in-out; }
  .nav-links button.plain::after { content:""; position:absolute; left:12px; right:12px; bottom:1px; height:2px; border-radius:2px;
    background:var(--blue); transform:scaleX(0); transform-origin:center; opacity:0;
    transition:transform .25s ease-in-out, opacity .25s ease-in-out; }
  .nav-links button.plain:hover { color:var(--ink); background:rgba(15,32,60,.05); }
  .nav-links button.plain:hover::after { transform:scaleX(.6); opacity:.55; }
  .nav-links button.plain.active { color:var(--ink); font-weight:600; transform:scale(1.08); letter-spacing:0; }
  .nav-links button.plain.active:hover { transform:scale(1.1); }
  .nav-links button.plain.active::after { transform:scaleX(1); opacity:1; height:2.5px; }
  .nav-cta { transform-origin:center center; }
  .nav-cta.active { transform:scale(1.07); font-weight:600 !important; box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,113,227,.36); }
  .nav-cta.active:hover { transform:scale(1.09); }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){ .nav-links button.plain.active, .nav-cta.active { transform:none; } }
  .nav-cta { box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,113,227,.26); transition:all .25s ease-in-out; }
  .nav-cta:hover { box-shadow:0 8px 22px rgba(0,113,227,.34); }
  .lang-btn { width:auto; min-width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:980px; gap:5px; padding:0 10px;
    font-family:inherit; font-size:12.5px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.02em; }
  .lang-btn .lg-code { text-transform:uppercase; }
  .lang-btn .lg-caret { opacity:.65; transition:transform .25s ease-in-out; }
  .lang.open .lg-caret { transform:rotate(180deg); }
  .lang-btn:hover { transform:none; color:var(--ink); background:var(--surface); border-color:var(--ink-3); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
  .lang-menu { display:flex; opacity:0; pointer-events:none; transform:translateY(-6px) scale(.97); transform-origin:top right;
    transition:opacity .22s ease-in-out, transform .22s ease-in-out; }
  .lang-menu.open { opacity:1; transform:none; pointer-events:auto; }
  .lang-menu button { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; }
  .lang-menu button.active::after { content:"\2713"; color:var(--blue); font-size:12px; }

  /* (5) bandas alternas */
  #page-inicio .hero { background:var(--surface); }
  #page-inicio .section-pad { background:var(--surface); }
  #page-nosotros { background:var(--tint-1); border-top:1px solid var(--tint-line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--tint-line); }
  #page-herramientas .tools-hero { background:var(--surface); border-bottom:1px solid var(--tint-line); }
  #page-herramientas > .wrap { background:var(--tint-1); padding-top:26px; }
  #page-herramientas .seg-wrap { background:var(--tint-1); margin:0; padding:26px 0 22px; }
  .cta-band { background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--tint-2),var(--panel)); border:1px solid var(--tint-line); }

  /* (6) foco por hover: la card enfocada resalta, las hermanas se atenuan */
  .hover-focus > * { transition:transform .3s var(--ease), opacity .3s var(--ease), box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease); }
  .hover-focus:hover > * { opacity:.65; }
  .hover-focus:hover > *:hover { opacity:1; transform:scale(1.02) translateY(-3px); box-shadow:var(--shadow-md); border-color:var(--border); }

  /* cards de Inicio y Quienes somos: escala protagonica y sombra elevada */
  .feature, .value { transform-origin:center center; will-change:transform;
    transition:transform .3s ease, box-shadow .3s ease, border-color .3s ease, opacity .3s ease; }
  .feature:hover, .value:hover,
  .cards-3.hover-focus:hover > .feature:hover, .values.hover-focus:hover > .value:hover {
    opacity:1; transform:scale(1.07) translateY(-6px); z-index:2;
    box-shadow:0 24px 50px rgba(15,32,60,.16), 0 6px 16px rgba(15,32,60,.08);
    border-color:rgba(0,113,227,.28);
  }
  .feature:hover .ic { transform:scale(1.08); background:rgba(0,113,227,.10); }
  .feature .ic { transition:transform .3s ease, background-color .3s ease; }
  .feature:active, .value:active { transform:scale(1.03) translateY(-3px); }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){ .feature:hover, .value:hover { transform:none; } }
  .value { cursor:default; }
  /* --- pestañas de Herramientas: estado activo evidente + transicion --- */
  .seg { position:relative; box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px var(--border-2); }
  .seg button { position:relative; z-index:1; padding:10px 20px; font-weight:500; }
  .seg button:hover { color:var(--ink); }
  .seg button.active { background:var(--blue); color:#fff; font-weight:600;
    box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,113,227,-0.0), 0 6px 18px rgba(0,113,227,.28);
    animation:segpop .32s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1); }
  @keyframes segpop { 0%{transform:scale(.94);} 60%{transform:scale(1.05);} 100%{transform:scale(1);} }
  .seg.hover-focus:hover > button.active { opacity:1; }
  #page-herramientas > .wrap > section { animation:tabIn .42s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1) both; }
  #page-herramientas > .wrap > section.from-left { animation-name:tabInLeft; }
  @keyframes tabIn { from{opacity:0; transform:translateX(34px) scale(.995);} to{opacity:1; transform:none;} }
  @keyframes tabInLeft { from{opacity:0; transform:translateX(-34px) scale(.995);} to{opacity:1; transform:none;} }
  #page-herramientas > .wrap > section.tab-out { animation:tabOut .2s ease-in both; }
  #page-herramientas > .wrap > section.tab-out.to-right { animation-name:tabOutRight; }
  @keyframes tabOut { from{opacity:1; transform:none;} to{opacity:0; transform:translateX(-28px);} }
  @keyframes tabOutRight { from{opacity:1; transform:none;} to{opacity:0; transform:translateX(28px);} }
  /* el bloque "Tu perfil / CV base" se refresca en sincronia con la herramienta activa */
  .prof-box { transition:box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease); }
  .prof-box.syncing { animation:profSync .62s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1); border-color:rgba(0,113,227,.35); }
  @keyframes profSync {
    0%   { opacity:1;  transform:scale(1);     box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
    28%  { opacity:.55; transform:scale(.988); box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(0,113,227,.10), var(--shadow-sm); }
    62%  { opacity:1;  transform:scale(1.004); box-shadow:0 0 0 5px rgba(0,113,227,.14), var(--shadow-md); }
    100% { opacity:1;  transform:scale(1);     box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
  }
  .prof-box .sync-tag { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:5px; margin-left:auto; font-size:11px; font-weight:600;
    letter-spacing:.02em; color:var(--blue); background:rgba(0,113,227,.09); border-radius:980px; padding:3px 9px;
    opacity:0; transform:translateY(-2px); transition:opacity .3s var(--ease), transform .3s var(--ease); pointer-events:none; }
  .prof-box.syncing .sync-tag { opacity:1; transform:none; }
  .prof-box.syncing .chips .chip { animation:chipIn .45s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1) both; }
  .prof-box.syncing .chips .chip:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.03s} .prof-box.syncing .chips .chip:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.06s}
  .prof-box.syncing .chips .chip:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.09s} .prof-box.syncing .chips .chip:nth-child(5){animation-delay:.12s}
  @keyframes chipIn { from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(4px) scale(.94);} to{opacity:1; transform:none;} }

  /* --- reveal: los elementos cobran vida al entrar en el viewport --- */
  .reveal { opacity:0; transform:translateY(24px); will-change:opacity, transform;
    transition:opacity .75s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), transform .75s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1); }
  .reveal.in { opacity:1; transform:none; }
  .reveal.rv-left  { transform:translateY(18px) translateX(-16px); }
  .reveal.rv-scale { transform:translateY(18px) scale(.97); }
  .reveal.in.rv-left, .reveal.in.rv-scale { transform:none; }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){ .reveal { opacity:1 !important; transform:none !important; } }

  /* --- rol opcional: chip + microcopy --- */
  .opt-tag { font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.03em; text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--ink-3); background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:980px; padding:3px 9px; }
  .field-hint { display:flex; gap:7px; align-items:flex-start; max-width:70ch; margin:0 0 20px;
    font-size:12.8px; line-height:1.5; color:var(--ink-2); transition:color .3s var(--ease); }
  .field-hint svg { flex-shrink:0; margin-top:2px; color:var(--blue); opacity:.85; }
  .field-hint.dimmed { color:var(--ink-3); }
  .generic-note { display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:flex-start; background:rgba(0,113,227,.06);
    border:1px solid rgba(0,113,227,.18); border-radius:12px; padding:11px 14px; font-size:13px;
    line-height:1.5; color:var(--ink-2); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .generic-note b { color:var(--ink); font-weight:600; }

  /* CTA de cierre de "Quienes somos" */
  .about-cta { text-align:center; margin-top:48px; padding-top:34px; border-top:1px solid var(--tint-line); }
  .about-cta p { font-size:17px; color:var(--ink-2); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .about-cta .btn { transition:transform .3s ease, box-shadow .3s ease, background-color .2s ease;
    box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,113,227,.24); }
  .about-cta .btn:hover { transform:scale(1.07) translateY(-2px); box-shadow:0 14px 32px rgba(0,113,227,.32); }

  .seg.hover-focus:hover > button { opacity:.6; }
  .seg.hover-focus:hover > button:hover { opacity:1; transform:scale(1.04); background:var(--surface); color:var(--ink); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
  .jobs.hover-focus:hover > .job:hover { transform:scale(1.01) translateY(-3px); }
  .role-grid.hover-focus:hover > .role-card:hover { transform:scale(1.01) translateY(-2px); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }

  /* (8)(9) hoja de CV — estilo ejecutivo / Harvard, A4 */
  .cv-sheet-wrap { margin-top:16px; }
  .cv-toolbar { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:12px; }
  .cv-toolbar .cv-hint { font-size:12.5px; color:var(--ink-3); max-width:46ch; line-height:1.45; }
  .cv-toolbar .pro-actions { margin-top:0; }
  .cv-doc { --cv-pad:54px; width:100%; max-width:794px; margin:0 auto; box-sizing:border-box;
    background:#fff; color:#111; border:1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius:6px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(15,32,60,.10); padding:var(--cv-pad) calc(var(--cv-pad) + 8px);
    font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, 'EB Garamond', Garamond, Georgia, serif;
    font-size:11.5pt; line-height:1.32; letter-spacing:0; text-align:left;
    overflow-wrap:anywhere; word-break:normal; hyphens:auto; }
  .cv-doc * { max-width:100%; }
  .cv-name { text-align:center; font-size:20pt; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:.05em; line-height:1.15; margin:0 0 7px; }
  .cv-contact { text-align:center; font-size:9.6pt; line-height:1.6; color:#333; margin:0; }
  .cv-contact span { white-space:nowrap; }
  .cv-contact .sep { color:#aaa; padding:0 6px; }
  .cv-sec { margin-top:15px; break-inside:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; }
  .cv-sec hr { border:none; border-top:.8px solid #333; margin:0 0 5px; }
  .cv-h { font-size:10.4pt; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.12em; margin:0 0 6px; }
  .cv-p { margin:0; text-align:justify; }
  .cv-item { margin-bottom:9px; break-inside:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; }
  .cv-item:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
  .cv-row { display:flex; align-items:baseline; justify-content:space-between; gap:16px; }
  .cv-row .l { font-weight:700; min-width:0; }
  .cv-row .r { flex-shrink:0; font-style:italic; font-size:10.4pt; white-space:nowrap; text-align:right; }
  .cv-bul { margin:4px 0 0; padding-left:18px; list-style:disc; }
  .cv-bul li { margin:0 0 3px; padding-left:3px; text-align:justify; }
  .cv-bul li::marker { font-size:.85em; }
  .cv-miss { color:#8a6d00; font-style:italic; font-size:10pt; text-align:left; }

  /* --- CV editable en vivo --- */
  .cv-doc [contenteditable] { outline:none; border-radius:3px; padding:0 2px; margin:0 -2px;
    transition:background-color .2s var(--ease), box-shadow .2s var(--ease); }
  .cv-doc [contenteditable]:hover { background:#f1f6fd; }
  .cv-doc [contenteditable]:focus { background:#e9f2ff; box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(0,113,227,.32); }
  .cv-doc [contenteditable]:empty::before { content:attr(data-ph); color:#bfc3cb; font-style:italic; }
  .cv-item { position:relative; }
  .cv-x { position:absolute; top:0; right:-24px; width:19px; height:19px; border:none; border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--panel); color:var(--ink-3); font-size:12px; line-height:1; cursor:pointer; opacity:0;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-family:var(--font-mono);
    transition:opacity .2s var(--ease), background-color .2s var(--ease), color .2s var(--ease); }
  .cv-item:hover > .cv-x, .cv-bul li:hover > .cv-x { opacity:1; }
  .cv-x:hover { background:var(--red-soft); color:var(--red); }
  .cv-bul li { position:relative; }
  .cv-bul li > .cv-x { top:-1px; right:-24px; }
  .cv-add { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; margin-top:5px; padding:2px 9px; border-radius:980px;
    border:1px dashed var(--border); background:transparent; color:var(--ink-3); cursor:pointer;
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:11px; font-weight:500; opacity:.5;
    transition:opacity .2s var(--ease), border-color .2s var(--ease), color .2s var(--ease), background-color .2s var(--ease); }
  .cv-sec:hover .cv-add, .cv-add:focus { opacity:1; }
  .cv-add:hover { border-color:var(--blue); color:var(--blue); background:rgba(0,113,227,.06); border-style:solid; }
  .cv-editbar { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:10px;
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:12.5px; color:var(--ink-3); }
  .cv-editbar .pill { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; background:var(--green-soft); color:var(--green);
    border-radius:980px; padding:4px 11px; font-size:11.5px; font-weight:600; }
  .cv-editbar .link-btn { font-size:12.5px; }
  .cv-editbar .cv-btn-sm { padding:6px 12px; font-size:12.5px; }
  .cv-editbar .cv-btn-sm:hover:not(:disabled) { border-color:var(--blue); color:var(--blue); }
  @media print { .cv-x, .cv-add, .cv-editbar, .cv-toolbar { display:none !important; } }
  @media (max-width:840px){
    .cv-doc { --cv-pad:28px; font-size:11pt; } .cv-name { font-size:17pt; }
    .cv-row { flex-wrap:wrap; gap:2px 12px; } .cv-row .r { white-space:normal; text-align:left; }
  }
  @media print {
    @page { size:A4; margin:16mm; }
    body * { visibility:hidden; }
    .cv-doc, .cv-doc * { visibility:visible; }
    .cv-doc { position:absolute; left:0; top:0; margin:0; padding:0; border:none; box-shadow:none; border-radius:0; max-width:none; }
  }

  /* ================================================================
     IDENTIDAD PROPIA DEL MODULO "HERRAMIENTAS"
     (jerarquia distinta de la navbar y look editorial-tech, no "panel de chat")
     ================================================================ */
  #page-herramientas {
    --accent:#0b5fff; --accent-deep:#15294d; --accent-soft:#eef3ff;
    --signal:#0e9f6e; --signal-soft:#e6f6ef; --line:#e4e9f2;
    --mono:ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
  }
  /* fondo con textura de puntos: se despega del blanco plano */
  #page-herramientas > .wrap {
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(21,41,77,.055) 1px, transparent 0) 0 0/22px 22px,
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--tint-1), #fff 620px);
    padding-top:30px; padding-bottom:40px;
  }
  #page-herramientas .tools-hero h1 { letter-spacing:-0.035em; }
  #page-herramientas .tools-hero h1::after {
    content:""; display:block; width:54px; height:4px; border-radius:4px; margin:16px auto 0;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-deep), var(--accent));
  }

  /* --- sub-navegacion: sin pastilla azul, subrayado deslizante (Opcion 1) --- */
  #page-herramientas .seg-wrap { background:transparent; padding:22px 0 6px; }
  .seg { position:relative; display:inline-flex; gap:4px; background:transparent; box-shadow:none;
    border-radius:0; padding:0 2px 10px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); overflow-x:auto; }
  .seg::after {                                  /* la linea que se desliza */
    content:""; position:absolute; left:var(--ind-x,0px); bottom:-1px; width:var(--ind-w,0px); height:3px;
    border-radius:3px; background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-deep), var(--accent));
    transition:left .38s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), width .38s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), opacity .25s ease;
    opacity:var(--ind-o,0);
  }
  .seg button { background:none !important; border:none; border-radius:8px; padding:9px 14px 12px;
    font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:#7c8595; letter-spacing:-0.005em;
    box-shadow:none !important; white-space:nowrap; cursor:pointer;
    transition:color .25s ease-in-out, transform .25s ease-in-out, opacity .25s ease-in-out; }
  .seg button:hover { color:var(--accent-deep); transform:none; background:none !important; }
  .seg button.active { color:var(--accent-deep) !important; font-weight:700; background:none !important;
    box-shadow:none !important; animation:none; transform:none; }
  .seg.hover-focus:hover > button { opacity:.55; }
  .seg.hover-focus:hover > button:hover, .seg.hover-focus:hover > button.active { opacity:1; transform:none; box-shadow:none !important; background:none !important; }

  /* --- paneles: tarjeta editorial, no bloque plano --- */
  #page-herramientas .card,
  #page-herramientas .job,
  #page-herramientas .adapted,
  #page-herramientas .improved,
  #page-herramientas .role-card,
  #page-herramientas .format-tip {
    position:relative; background:#fff; border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:20px 20px 20px 5px;                       /* esquina firmada, asimetrica */
    box-shadow:0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,.9) inset, 0 14px 34px rgba(15,32,60,.07), 0 2px 6px rgba(15,32,60,.04);
    transition:transform .3s var(--ease), box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s var(--ease);
  }
  #page-herramientas .card::before,
  #page-herramientas .job::before {
    content:""; position:absolute; left:0; top:22px; bottom:22px; width:3px; border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent-deep), var(--accent));
    opacity:0; transform:scaleY(.4); transform-origin:center;
    transition:opacity .3s var(--ease), transform .3s var(--ease);
  }
  #page-herramientas .card:hover::before,
  #page-herramientas .job:hover::before { opacity:1; transform:scaleY(1); }
  #page-herramientas .job:hover { transform:translateY(-3px); box-shadow:0 22px 46px rgba(15,32,60,.11); border-color:#d5dfef; }

  /* encabezado de panel con numeral tipo revista */
  #page-herramientas .panel-head { position:relative; padding-left:0; margin-bottom:18px; }
  #page-herramientas .panel-head h2 { display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:11px; font-size:27px; letter-spacing:-0.03em; }
  #page-herramientas section[data-step] .panel-head h2::before {
    content:attr(data-num); font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.12em;
    color:var(--accent); background:var(--accent-soft); border-radius:6px; padding:4px 7px; transform:translateY(-3px);
  }
  #page-herramientas .panel-head p { color:#5d6675; }
  .tool-lead { color:var(--accent-deep); font-weight:600; }
  .tool-lead::before { background:linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent-deep), var(--accent)); opacity:1; width:3px; height:16px; }

  /* eyebrows y datos en monoespaciada: sello de marca */
  #page-herramientas .eyebrow, #page-herramientas .subhead, #page-herramientas .cvh,
  #page-herramientas .adapted .tape, #page-herramientas .improved .tape, #page-herramientas .format-tip h5 {
    font-family:var(--mono); font-size:10.5px; letter-spacing:.14em; text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  #page-herramientas .stat-pill, #page-herramientas .credits { font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.02em; border-radius:8px; }
  #page-herramientas .ring-num b { font-family:var(--mono); }
  #page-herramientas .chip { border-radius:7px; background:var(--accent-soft); color:var(--accent-deep); font-weight:600; font-size:12.5px; }
  #page-herramientas .kw { border-radius:7px; font-family:var(--mono); font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.01em; }
  #page-herramientas .kw.has { background:var(--signal-soft); color:#0b7a54; }
  #page-herramientas .kw-box { background:#fbfcfe; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:16px 16px 16px 4px; }
  #page-herramientas .sw-box { border-radius:16px 16px 16px 4px; }
  #page-herramientas .role-card { background:#fff; }
  #page-herramientas .qbox { border-radius:12px 12px 12px 4px; background:#fbfcfe; }

  /* botones de accion del modulo: cuadrados, no pastillas (la pastilla es de la navbar) */
  #page-herramientas .btn { border-radius:12px; }
  #page-herramientas .btn-blue { background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-deep), var(--accent));
    box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(11,95,255,.26); }
  #page-herramientas .btn-blue:hover { box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(11,95,255,.34); transform:translateY(-1px); }
  #page-herramientas .act-btn, #page-herramientas .reader-btn { border-radius:10px; }
  #page-herramientas .reader-btn.active { background:var(--accent-deep); border-color:var(--accent-deep); }
  #page-herramientas .reader-card { border-radius:16px 16px 16px 4px; }
  #page-herramientas .reader-card.active { border-color:var(--accent); background:var(--accent-soft);
    box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(11,95,255,.12), 0 14px 30px rgba(15,32,60,.10); }
  #page-herramientas .reader-card.active .rc-ic { background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-deep), var(--accent)); }

  /* caption de ayuda (filtros vacios) */
  .helper-note { display:flex; gap:7px; align-items:flex-start; max-width:74ch;
    margin:16px 0 0; padding:9px 12px; border-radius:10px 10px 10px 3px;
    background:#f7f9fd; border:1px solid var(--line); border-left:3px solid var(--accent);
    font-size:11.8px; line-height:1.5; color:#5d6675; }
  .helper-note::before { content:"i"; flex-shrink:0; width:14px; height:14px; border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--accent); color:#fff; font-family:var(--mono); font-size:9.5px; font-weight:700;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-top:1px; }

  /* fuera las flechas / scrollbar de la barra de subsecciones */
  .seg { scrollbar-width:none; -ms-overflow-style:none; }
  .seg::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; width:0; height:0; }

  /* ---- MODO ENFOQUE: al abrir una herramienta, la barra de subsecciones se retira ---- */
  #page-herramientas .seg-wrap {
    overflow:hidden; max-height:120px; opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);
    transition:max-height .42s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), opacity .3s ease-in-out,
               transform .42s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), padding .42s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1);
  }
  #page-herramientas.focus .seg-wrap {
    max-height:0; opacity:0; transform:translateY(-10px); padding-top:0; padding-bottom:0; pointer-events:none;
  }
  .tools-back-row {
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;
    max-height:0; opacity:0; transform:translateY(-6px); overflow:hidden; pointer-events:none;
    transition:max-height .42s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), opacity .3s ease-in-out .06s, transform .42s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), margin .42s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1);
  }
  #page-herramientas.focus .tools-back-row { max-height:60px; opacity:1; transform:none; pointer-events:auto; margin:0 0 18px; }
  .tools-back {
    display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; cursor:pointer; font-family:inherit;
    font-size:12.8px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.005em; color:#5d6675;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,.72); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:980px;
    padding:6px 13px 6px 9px; backdrop-filter:saturate(1.4) blur(8px);
    transition:color .25s ease-in-out, border-color .25s ease-in-out, background-color .25s ease-in-out, transform .25s ease-in-out, box-shadow .25s ease-in-out; }
  .tools-back svg { transition:transform .25s ease-in-out; }
  .tools-back:hover { color:var(--accent-deep); border-color:var(--accent); background:#fff;
    box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,32,60,.08); transform:translateX(-2px); }
  .tools-back:hover svg { transform:translateX(-2px); }
  .tools-current { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.13em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); }
  .tools-current::before { content:""; width:5px; height:5px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--accent); }

  @media (max-width:720px){
    #page-herramientas .panel-head h2 { font-size:22px; }
    .seg { padding-bottom:8px; }
    .tools-back { font-size:12px; }
  }

  /* ================================================================
     SISTEMA TIPOGRAFICO Y DE CONTENEDORES PROPIO DE MATCHAPPLY
     Display: Bricolage Grotesque (editorial, ancha, con caracter)
     Texto:   Manrope (geometrica, nada que ver con Inter)
     Datos:   JetBrains Mono (etiquetas, numeros, metadatos)
     Cajas:   papel recortado — esquinas rectas, filete fino, sombra dura desplazada
     ================================================================ */
  :root {
    --font-display:'Bricolage Grotesque', 'Manrope', system-ui, sans-serif;
    --font-body:'Manrope', system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    --font-mono:'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
    --ink-line:#dbe2ec;
  }
  body, button, input, textarea, select, .btn, .nav-links button {
    font-family:var(--font-body); letter-spacing:-0.005em;
  }
  h1, h2, h3, h4, h5,
  .hero h1, .section-title, .about-hero h1, .about-quote, .tools-hero h1,
  .panel-head h2, .feature h3, .value h4, .cta-band h2, .modal h3, .nav-logo strong, .bot-head b {
    font-family:var(--font-display); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.025em;
  }
  .hero h1, .about-hero h1, .tools-hero h1 { font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-0.04em; line-height:1.02; }
  .hero .eyebrow, .about-hero .eyebrow, .eyebrow, .subhead, .chips-label, .tool-lead,
  .plan-badge, .top-flag, .partner, .score-tag, .prolock, .tools-current, .cv-editbar .pill {
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:10.5px;
  }
  .tool-lead { font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.09em; }
  .hero .eyebrow { font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.16em; }
  .about-quote { font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.03em; }
  .stat-pill, .credits, .meta, .ring-num b, .kw, .chip, .cv-toolbar .cv-hint, .helper-note, .disclaimer.ai {
    font-family:var(--font-mono);
  }
  .meta, .kw, .chip { font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.005em; }
  .disclaimer.ai, .helper-note { letter-spacing:.01em; }
  .btn, .act-btn, .seg button, .nav-links button { font-family:var(--font-body); font-weight:600; }
  .cv-doc, .cv-doc * { font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, 'EB Garamond', Garamond, Georgia, serif !important; }
  .cv-doc .cv-x, .cv-doc .cv-add { font-family:var(--font-mono) !important; }

  /* ---- CAJAS: papel recortado, no burbuja de chat ---- */
  .feature, .value {
    border-radius:4px; border:1px solid var(--ink-line); box-shadow:none;
    background:#fff; padding:30px 26px 28px; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  }
  .feature::before, .value::before {
    content:""; position:absolute; inset:0 auto auto 0; width:100%; height:3px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#15294d,#0b5fff); transform:scaleX(0); transform-origin:left;
    transition:transform .38s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1);
  }
  .feature:hover::before, .value:hover::before { transform:scaleX(1); }
  .feature:hover, .value:hover,
  .cards-3.hover-focus:hover > .feature:hover, .values.hover-focus:hover > .value:hover {
    transform:translate(-3px,-3px); border-color:#15294d;
    box-shadow:8px 8px 0 rgba(21,41,77,.08);            /* sombra dura desplazada: firma de marca */
  }
  .feature .ic { border-radius:4px; background:#eef3ff; }
  .cta-band { border-radius:6px; }

  #page-herramientas .card,
  #page-herramientas .job,
  #page-herramientas .adapted,
  #page-herramientas .improved,
  #page-herramientas .role-card,
  #page-herramientas .format-tip,
  #page-herramientas .kw-box,
  #page-herramientas .sw-box,
  #page-herramientas .qbox,
  #page-herramientas .reader-card {
    border-radius:4px; border:1px solid var(--ink-line);
    box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(15,32,60,.04);
  }
  #page-herramientas .card::before, #page-herramientas .job::before { top:0; bottom:auto; left:0; width:100%; height:3px;
    border-radius:0; transform:scaleX(0); transform-origin:left;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#15294d,#0b5fff);
    transition:transform .38s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1), opacity .2s ease; opacity:1; }
  #page-herramientas .card:hover::before, #page-herramientas .job:hover::before { transform:scaleX(1); }
  #page-herramientas .job:hover, #page-herramientas .reader-card:hover {
    transform:translate(-3px,-3px); border-color:#15294d; box-shadow:8px 8px 0 rgba(21,41,77,.07);
  }
  #page-herramientas .reader-card.active {
    border-color:#0b5fff; box-shadow:5px 5px 0 rgba(11,95,255,.16); transform:none; background:#f5f8ff;
  }
  #page-herramientas .btn, #page-herramientas .act-btn, #page-herramientas .reader-btn,
  #page-herramientas .cv-btn-sm, .helper-note, .disclaimer.ai, .tools-back { border-radius:3px; }
  #page-herramientas .btn-blue { box-shadow:4px 4px 0 rgba(11,95,255,.20); transition:transform .22s ease, box-shadow .22s ease; }
  #page-herramientas .btn-blue:hover { transform:translate(-2px,-2px); box-shadow:6px 6px 0 rgba(11,95,255,.24); }
  #page-herramientas .btn-blue:active { transform:translate(0,0); box-shadow:2px 2px 0 rgba(11,95,255,.24); }
  #page-herramientas .chip, #page-herramientas .kw, #page-herramientas .stat-pill,
  #page-herramientas .credits, #page-herramientas .score-tag, #page-herramientas .top-flag { border-radius:3px; }
  .tools-back { border-radius:3px; }
  #page-herramientas .card { padding:26px 26px 24px; }

  /* la navbar mantiene su lenguaje de pastillas (jerarquia distinta, a proposito) */
  .nav-cta, .acct-btn, .lang-btn { border-radius:980px !important; }
  .modal { border-radius:6px; }
  .bot-head { border-radius:0; }
  #botPanel { border-radius:6px; }
  #botBtn { border-radius:6px; box-shadow:5px 5px 0 rgba(21,41,77,.22); }
  #botBtn:hover { transform:translate(-2px,-2px); box-shadow:7px 7px 0 rgba(21,41,77,.26); }
  .bmsg { border-radius:4px !important; }

  /* ---- voz tipografica propia en los textos clave ---- */
  /* "Tu perfil / CV base" */
  #page-herramientas .prof-box .eyebrow {
    font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:17px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-0.03em;
    text-transform:none; color:var(--accent-deep);
  }
  /* microcopy de cada subseccion: "Ajustamos tu CV a las palabras clave..." */
  .tool-lead {
    font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:16px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:-0.02em;
    text-transform:none; color:#3a4a66; font-style:italic; align-items:flex-start; line-height:1.35;
  }
  .tool-lead::before { height:19px; margin-top:2px; }
  /* disclaimer de IA */
  .disclaimer.ai {
    font-family:var(--font-body); font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.045em;
    text-transform:uppercase; color:#93794a; background:transparent; border:none; border-left:2px solid rgba(154,106,0,.35);
    border-radius:0; padding:2px 0 2px 9px;
  }
  .disclaimer.ai:hover { background:transparent; color:#7a5500; border-left-color:rgba(154,106,0,.6); }
  .disclaimer.ai svg { opacity:.6; }
  /* "Lo que ya detectamos en tu CV" y demas titulos de caja */
  #page-herramientas .kw-box h5, #page-herramientas .sw-box h5 {
    font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:15px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.02em; text-transform:none;
  }
  /* "Resumen general" / "Resumen a medida" */
  #page-herramientas .adapted .tape, #page-herramientas .improved .tape {
    font-family:var(--font-display); font-size:13px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:.02em; text-transform:none;
    color:var(--accent-deep); background:linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 62%, rgba(11,95,255,.18) 0);
    padding:0 2px 1px;
  }
  #page-herramientas .adapted h5, #page-herramientas .improved h5 {
    font-family:var(--font-display); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.025em; font-size:20px;
  }

  /* ---- paywall del editor manual ---- */
  .cv-doc.locked [contenteditable] { cursor:default; }
  .cv-doc.locked [contenteditable]:hover, .cv-doc.locked [contenteditable]:focus { background:transparent; box-shadow:none; }
  .cv-doc.locked .cv-x, .cv-doc.locked .cv-add { display:none !important; }
  .cv-lock-btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:6px; cursor:pointer; font-family:var(--font-body);
    font-size:12.5px; font-weight:700; padding:6px 12px; border-radius:3px; color:#5b2fb8;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11,95,255,.10), rgba(123,47,247,.12));
    border:1px solid rgba(123,47,247,.28);
    transition:transform .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease, background-color .25s ease; }
  .cv-lock-btn:hover { transform:translate(-2px,-2px); box-shadow:4px 4px 0 rgba(123,47,247,.18); }
  .cv-lock-btn .crown { font-size:12px; }
  .cv-edit-on { border-color:var(--accent) !important; color:var(--accent-deep) !important;
    background:var(--accent-soft) !important; }

  /* ---- registro seguro: fuerza de contraseña + verificación por código ---- */
  .pw-rules { display:grid; gap:5px; margin:-4px 0 14px; }
  .pw-rule { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:10.5px;
    letter-spacing:.04em; color:var(--ink-3); transition:color .25s ease-in-out; }
  .pw-rule .dot { width:13px; height:13px; border-radius:3px; border:1.5px solid var(--border);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0;
    transition:background-color .25s ease-in-out, border-color .25s ease-in-out, transform .25s ease-in-out; }
  .pw-rule .dot svg { opacity:0; transition:opacity .2s ease-in-out; }
  .pw-rule.ok { color:#0b7a54; }
  .pw-rule.ok .dot { background:#0e9f6e; border-color:#0e9f6e; transform:scale(1.06); }
  .pw-rule.ok .dot svg { opacity:1; }
  .pw-bar { height:4px; border-radius:2px; background:var(--border-2); overflow:hidden; margin:8px 0 12px; }
  .pw-bar span { display:block; height:100%; width:0%; border-radius:2px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#c0362c,#9a6a00,#0e9f6e); transition:width .35s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1); }
  .fld.err input { border-color:var(--red); box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(192,54,44,.12); }
  .fld-msg { font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:10.5px; letter-spacing:.04em; margin-top:5px; color:var(--red); display:none; }
  .fld.err .fld-msg { display:block; }
  .fld.match input { border-color:#0e9f6e; }

  .otp-head { text-align:center; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .otp-ic { width:48px; height:48px; border-radius:4px; margin:0 auto 14px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#15294d,#0b5fff); color:#fff; box-shadow:5px 5px 0 rgba(11,95,255,.16); }
  .otp-mail { font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:12px; color:var(--ink); background:var(--panel);
    border-radius:3px; padding:3px 8px; display:inline-block; margin-top:4px; }
  .otp-row { display:flex; gap:8px; justify-content:center; margin:20px 0 8px; }
  .otp-row input { width:46px; height:56px; text-align:center; font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:22px; font-weight:700;
    border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:3px; background:#fff; color:var(--ink);
    transition:border-color .2s ease-in-out, box-shadow .2s ease-in-out, transform .2s ease-in-out; }
  .otp-row input:focus { outline:none; border-color:#0b5fff; box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(11,95,255,.14); transform:translateY(-2px); }
  .otp-row.bad input { border-color:var(--red); animation:otpShake .35s ease-in-out; }
  @keyframes otpShake { 0%,100%{transform:translateX(0)} 25%{transform:translateX(-5px)} 75%{transform:translateX(5px)} }
  .otp-meta { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:10.5px; letter-spacing:.04em; color:var(--ink-3); margin-top:10px; }
  .otp-meta b { color:var(--ink); }
  .otp-err { color:var(--red); font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:11px; text-align:center; margin-top:10px; min-height:14px; }
  .otp-demo { margin-top:14px; padding:9px 12px; border-left:2px solid rgba(11,95,255,.4); background:rgba(11,95,255,.05);
    font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:10.5px; line-height:1.6; color:#41506b; }
  .otp-demo b { font-size:14px; letter-spacing:.22em; color:#0b5fff; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="top">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <div class="nav-logo" onclick="showPage('inicio')">
      <span class="mark" id="navMark"></span>
      <strong>MatchApply</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <div class="nav-links">
        <button class="plain" data-page="inicio" onclick="showPage('inicio')" data-i18n="nav_home">Inicio</button>
        <button class="plain" data-page="nosotros" onclick="showPage('nosotros')" data-i18n="nav_about">¿Quiénes somos?</button>
        <button class="nav-cta" data-page="herramientas" onclick="showPage('herramientas')" data-i18n="nav_tools">Herramientas</button>
      </div>
      <span id="acctArea"></span>
      <div class="lang" id="lang">
        <button class="lang-btn" id="langBtn" aria-label="Idioma / Language" aria-haspopup="listbox" aria-expanded="false" onclick="toggleLangMenu(event)">
          <svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M3 12h18"/><path d="M12 3c2.5 2.5 3.8 5.7 3.8 9s-1.3 6.5-3.8 9c-2.5-2.5-3.8-5.7-3.8-9s1.3-6.5 3.8-9z"/></svg>
          <span class="lg-code" id="langCode">es</span>
          <svg class="lg-caret" width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="lang-menu" id="langMenu">
          <button data-l="es" onclick="setLang('es')">Español</button>
          <button data-l="en" onclick="setLang('en')">English</button>
          <button data-l="fr" onclick="setLang('fr')">Français</button>
          <button data-l="pt" onclick="setLang('pt')">Português</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- INICIO -->
<section class="page active" id="page-inicio">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-logo" id="heroLogo"></div>
    <div class="eyebrow" data-i18n="hero_eyebrow">Obsesionados con tu búsqueda</div>
    <h1 data-i18n="hero_title">Encontrá trabajo y llegá preparado</h1>
    <p class="sub" data-i18n="hero_sub">MatchApply encuentra las ofertas donde de verdad encajás, adapta tu CV a cada búsqueda y, con un solo clic, prepara y envía todas tus postulaciones.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <button class="btn btn-blue" onclick="showPage('herramientas')" data-i18n="hero_start">Comenzar</button>
      <button class="btn-link" onclick="showPage('nosotros')" data-i18n="hero_more">Conocé más ›</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wrap section-pad">
    <h2 class="section-title" data-i18n="feat_title">Todo lo que necesitás para postularte mejor</h2>
    <p class="section-intro" data-i18n="feat_intro">Herramientas para dejar de mandar el mismo CV a todos lados y empezar a postularte con criterio.</p>
    <div class="cards-3 hover-focus">
      <div class="feature"><div class="ic"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0071e3" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20v-6M6 20v-3M18 20v-9"/><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="1.4"/><circle cx="6" cy="13" r="1.4"/><circle cx="18" cy="7" r="1.4"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="f1_h">Match inteligente</h3><p data-i18n="f1_p">Un puntaje de 0 a 100 que compara tu perfil con cada oferta, con razones concretas.</p></div>
      <div class="feature"><div class="ic"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0071e3" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6M9 13l2 2 4-4"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="f2_h">CV a medida</h3><p data-i18n="f2_p">Adaptamos tu currículum a las palabras clave que cada búsqueda necesita, sin tocar tu versión base.</p></div>
      <div class="feature"><div class="ic"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0071e3" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-4 12.7V17h8v-2.3A7 7 0 0 0 12 2zM9 21h6M10 17v4M14 17v4"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="f3_h">Listo para la entrevista</h3><p data-i18n="f3_p">Qué se valora en cada puesto, qué reforzar y las preguntas más probables.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- NOSOTROS (queda debajo de Inicio, se llega por scroll) -->
<section class="page active" id="page-nosotros">
  <div class="about-hero"><div class="eyebrow" data-i18n="ab_eyebrow">¿Quiénes somos?</div><h1 data-i18n="ab_title">Creemos que buscar trabajo puede ser distinto.</h1></div>
  <div class="narrow section-pad" style="padding-top:20px">
    <div class="about-body">
      <p class="lead" data-i18n="ab_p1">MatchApply nació de una convicción simple: el tiempo de quien busca empleo vale, y hoy se desperdicia. Cada vacante recibe cientos de postulaciones, y la mayoría termina enviando el mismo currículum a todos lados, sin saber en qué búsquedas tiene chances reales.</p>
      <p data-i18n="ab_p2">Nos propusimos cambiar eso con herramientas concretas: un puntaje que compara tu perfil con cada oferta, un asistente que adapta tu CV a lo que cada búsqueda pide, y una guía que te prepara para la entrevista. Todo a partir de un perfil que cargás una sola vez.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-quote"><p class="q" data-i18n="ab_quote_txt">“Postularse debería costar tiempo en las entrevistas, no en los formularios.”</p><span class="by" data-i18n="ab_quote_by">Nuestra premisa</span></div>
    <div class="about-body"><p data-i18n="ab_p3">Nuestra obsesión es una sola: que postularte se sienta distinto. Cada detalle —el puntaje, el CV que se adapta solo, la preparación para la entrevista— existe para que llegues más lejos con menos desgaste. Buscamos que la experiencia esté a la altura del trabajo que querés conseguir.</p></div>
    <hr class="soft" />
    <div class="values hover-focus">
      <div class="value"><h4 data-i18n="val1_h">Tu tiempo primero</h4><p data-i18n="val1_p">Te ayudamos a enfocar el esfuerzo donde de verdad tenés oportunidades.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><h4 data-i18n="val2_h">Criterio, no volumen</h4><p data-i18n="val2_p">No se trata de postularse a todo, sino de postularse bien.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><h4 data-i18n="val3_h">Una experiencia premium</h4><p data-i18n="val3_p">Herramientas de nivel profesional para que cada postulación tuya juegue en primera.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-cta">
      <p data-i18n="ab_cta_p">Todo esto ya está esperándote del otro lado.</p>
      <button class="btn btn-blue" onclick="goTools()" data-i18n="ab_btn">Probar las herramientas</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HERRAMIENTAS -->
<section class="page" id="page-herramientas">
  <div class="tools-hero"><h1 data-i18n="tools_h">Tus herramientas</h1><p data-i18n="tools_p">Cargá tu perfil una vez y usalo en todas. Elegí por dónde empezar.</p></div>
  <div class="seg-wrap">
    <div class="seg hover-focus" id="seg">
      <button class="active" data-tab="auto" onclick="switchTab('auto')" data-i18n="tab_auto">Postulación automática</button>
      <button data-tab="matches" onclick="switchTab('matches')" data-i18n="tab_matches">Ofertas</button>
      <button data-tab="adapter" onclick="switchTab('adapter')" data-i18n="tab_adapter">CV a medida</button>
      <button data-tab="analysis" onclick="switchTab('analysis')" data-i18n="tab_analysis">Diagnóstico</button>
      <button data-tab="role" onclick="switchTab('role')" data-i18n="tab_role">Entrevista</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wrap" style="padding-bottom:20px">
    <div class="tools-back-row" id="toolsBackRow">
      <button class="tools-back" onclick="exitFocus()" aria-label="Ver todas las herramientas">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="tools_all">Ver todas las herramientas</span>
      </button>
      <span class="tools-current" id="toolsCurrent"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="card prof-box">
      <div class="label-row">
        <span class="icon-chip"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6e6e73" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6M8 13h8M8 17h8"/></svg></span>
        <span class="eyebrow" data-i18n="prof_label">Tu perfil / CV base</span>
        <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm prof-upload" onclick="document.getElementById('cvFile').click()">
          <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4M17 8l-5-5-5 5M12 3v12"/></svg>
          <span data-i18n="prof_upload">Subir CV (PDF/DOCX)</span>
        </button>
        <input type="file" id="cvFile" accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx" style="display:none" onchange="handleCV(this)" />
        <span class="sync-tag" id="profSyncTag" data-i18n="prof_sync">Adaptando tu perfil…</span>
      </div>
      <textarea id="profile" rows="4" data-i18n-ph="prof_ph">Desarrollador/a Full Stack con 3 años de experiencia. Stack principal: React, JavaScript, Node.js y PostgreSQL. Manejo básico de Python y algo de diseño en Figma. Experiencia armando APIs REST, interfaces responsivas y trabajando en equipos ágiles. Inglés nivel B2.</textarea>
      <div class="cv-status" id="cvStatus"></div>
      <div class="chips" id="chips"></div>
    </div>

    <section data-step id="tab-auto">
<div class="disclaimer ai" style="margin-top:0"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg><span data-i18n="ai_disclaimer">La IA puede cometer errores; revisá siempre los datos. Jamás recomendamos mentir en tu CV.</span></div>
      <p class="tool-lead" data-i18n="lead_auto">Buscamos ofertas compatibles y dejamos cada postulación lista con tu CV.</p>
      <div class="panel-head"><h2 data-num="01" data-i18n="ap_h">Postulación automática</h2><p data-i18n="ap_p">Decinos qué buscás y nos encargamos del resto: buscamos ofertas compatibles en tiempo real y, con un solo clic, preparamos y enviamos todas tus postulaciones usando tu CV.</p></div>
      <div class="card">
        <div style="margin-bottom:22px"><span style="display:block;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px" data-i18n="ap_mod">Modalidad de trabajo</span>
          <div class="reader-toggle" style="margin-bottom:0" id="apMod">
            <button class="reader-btn active" data-v="remoto" onclick="togglePref('mod','remoto',this)" data-i18n="ap_remote">Remoto</button>
            <button class="reader-btn" data-v="hibrido" onclick="togglePref('mod','hibrido',this)" data-i18n="ap_hybrid">Híbrido</button>
            <button class="reader-btn" data-v="presencial" onclick="togglePref('mod','presencial',this)" data-i18n="ap_onsite">Presencial</button>
          </div></div>
        <div style="margin-bottom:22px"><span style="display:block;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px" data-i18n="ap_jor">Jornada</span>
          <div class="reader-toggle" style="margin-bottom:0" id="apJor">
            <button class="reader-btn active" data-v="full" onclick="togglePref('jor','full',this)" data-i18n="ap_full">Full-time</button>
            <button class="reader-btn" data-v="part" onclick="togglePref('jor','part',this)" data-i18n="ap_part">Part-time</button>
          </div></div>
        <div style="margin-bottom:8px"><span style="display:block;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:10px" data-i18n="ap_loc">Ubicación o zona horaria</span>
          <input class="js" id="apLoc" type="text" value="LatAm" style="width:100%;max-width:360px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:11px 14px;font-family:inherit;font-size:15px" /></div>
        <p class="helper-note" data-i18n="ap_nofilter">
          Si no seleccionás ninguna opción, no aplicamos ninguna restricción: buscamos de forma masiva cualquier oferta disponible que sea compatible con tu perfil.
        </p>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:8px;padding-top:18px;border-top:1px solid var(--border-2)">
          <button class="btn btn-blue" onclick="runAutopilot()" data-i18n="ap_btn">Buscar y postularme · 1 clic</button>
          <span style="font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-3)" data-i18n="ap_note">Usa tu CV de arriba. Vos podés revisar y confirmar cada envío.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section data-step id="tab-matches" class="hidden">
      <p class="tool-lead" data-i18n="lead_matches">Vemos en qué búsquedas tenés chances reales y por qué.</p>
      <div class="panel-head"><h2 data-num="02" data-i18n="m_h">Ofertas ordenadas por compatibilidad</h2><p data-i18n="m_p">Analizamos tu perfil contra cada búsqueda y le asignamos un puntaje de 0 a 100 con sus razones. Postulate a una o seleccioná varias para aplicar en conjunto.</p></div>
      <div class="disclaimer ai"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg><span data-i18n="ai_disclaimer">La IA puede cometer errores; revisá siempre los datos. Jamás recomendamos mentir en tu CV.</span></div>
      <div class="row-between">
        <button class="btn btn-blue btn-sm" id="analyzeBtn" onclick="analyzeAll()"><span id="analyzeLabel" data-i18n="m_analyze">Analizar mis oportunidades</span></button>
        <div class="stats hidden" id="stats"><span class="stat-pill"><b id="scored">0</b>/<span id="total">6</span> <span data-i18n="m_stat_analyzed">analizadas</span></span><span class="stat-pill"><b class="g" id="excellent">0</b> <span data-i18n="m_stat_excellent">excelentes</span></span></div>
      </div>
      <div id="batchBar"></div>
      <div class="jobs hover-focus" id="jobs" style="margin-top:14px"></div>
    </section>

    <section data-step id="tab-adapter" class="hidden">
      <p class="tool-lead" data-i18n="lead_adapter">Ajustamos tu CV a las palabras clave del puesto que elijas.</p>
      <div class="panel-head"><h2 data-num="03" data-i18n="ad_h">Tu CV, a medida de cada búsqueda</h2><p data-i18n="ad_p">Elegí una oferta y te mostramos qué palabras clave ya tenés, cuáles conviene sumar y un resumen adaptado. Tu CV base queda intacto.</p></div>
      <div class="disclaimer ai"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg><span data-i18n="ai_disclaimer">La IA puede cometer errores; revisá siempre los datos. Jamás recomendamos mentir en tu CV.</span></div>
      <div class="selrow" style="margin-bottom:6px">
        <label data-i18n="ad_for">Adaptar para:</label>
        <select class="js" id="adapterSel" onchange="renderAdapter()"></select>
        <span class="opt-tag" data-i18n="ad_optional">Opcional</span>
      </div>
      <p class="field-hint" id="adapterHint">
        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18h6M10 22h4"/><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-4 12.7V16h8v-1.3A7 7 0 0 0 12 2z"/></svg>
        <span data-i18n="ad_optional_hint">Podés seguir sin elegir puesto y adaptamos igual tu CV. Pero si nos decís a qué apuntás, el diagnóstico, las palabras clave y el resumen salen muchísimo más precisos y personalizados.</span>
      </p>
      <div id="adapterBody"></div>
    </section>

    <section data-step id="tab-analysis" class="hidden">
      <p class="tool-lead" data-i18n="lead_analysis">Te decimos qué funciona, qué falta y te devolvemos una versión prolija.</p>
      <div class="panel-head"><h2 data-num="04" data-i18n="an_h">Diagnóstico de tu CV</h2><p data-i18n="an_p">Un mismo CV no se lee igual si lo evalúa un cazatalentos, un área de RRHH o un sistema automático. Elegí el evaluador y ajustamos las recomendaciones. También generamos una versión mejorada.</p></div>
      <div class="disclaimer ai"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg><span data-i18n="ai_disclaimer">La IA puede cometer errores; revisá siempre los datos. Jamás recomendamos mentir en tu CV.</span></div>
      <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:10px" data-i18n="reader_pick">¿Quién va a leer tu CV?</div>
      <div class="reader-cards" id="readerToggle" role="radiogroup">
        <button class="reader-card active" role="radio" aria-checked="true" data-reader="hh" onclick="setReader('hh')">
          <span class="rc-dot"></span>
          <span class="rc-top"><span class="rc-ic"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="M21 21l-4.3-4.3"/></svg></span><h5 data-i18n="reader_hh">Cazatalentos</h5></span>
          <p data-i18n="reader_hh_d">Escanea en segundos: busca seniority y encaje con su cliente.</p>
        </button>
        <button class="reader-card" role="radio" aria-checked="false" data-reader="hr" onclick="setReader('hr')">
          <span class="rc-dot"></span>
          <span class="rc-top"><span class="rc-ic"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg></span><h5 data-i18n="reader_hr">RRHH interno</h5></span>
          <p data-i18n="reader_hr_d">Chequea requisitos del aviso y períodos sin explicar.</p>
        </button>
        <button class="reader-card" role="radio" aria-checked="false" data-reader="bot" onclick="setReader('bot')">
          <span class="rc-dot"></span>
          <span class="rc-top"><span class="rc-ic"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="8" width="16" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M12 8V4H8M2 14h2M20 14h2M9 13v2M15 13v2"/></svg></span><h5 data-i18n="reader_bot">Sistema ATS</h5></span>
          <p data-i18n="reader_bot_d">Lee texto plano: se traga columnas, tablas e imágenes mal.</p>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div id="analysisBody"></div>
    </section>

    <section data-step id="tab-role" class="hidden">
      <p class="tool-lead" data-i18n="lead_role">Qué van a evaluar y qué preguntas te esperan en ese puesto.</p>
      <div class="panel-head"><h2 data-num="05" data-i18n="role_h">Preparación para la entrevista</h2><p data-i18n="role_p">Elegí el puesto al que apuntás: qué se valora, qué conviene reforzar y cómo llegar preparado.</p></div>
      <div class="disclaimer ai"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg><span data-i18n="ai_disclaimer">La IA puede cometer errores; revisá siempre los datos. Jamás recomendamos mentir en tu CV.</span></div>
      <div class="selrow"><label data-i18n="role_puesto">Puesto:</label><select class="js" id="roleSel" onchange="renderRole()"></select></div>
      <div id="roleBody"></div>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="foot"><div class="wrap" data-i18n="foot">MatchApply · Versión demo — el puntaje y los textos se calculan localmente en tu navegador y los datos son de ejemplo. En producción el cálculo corre en un servidor con un modelo de lenguaje y las ofertas provienen de una fuente real.</div></footer>

<!-- Chatbot -->
<button id="botBtn" aria-label="Asistente"><span class="dot"></span><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/><path d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01"/></svg></button>
<div id="botPanel">
  <div class="bot-head"><span class="ava"><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 8V4H8"/><rect x="4" y="8" width="16" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M2 14h2M20 14h2M15 13v2M9 13v2"/></svg></span><div><b data-i18n="bot_name">Asistente MatchApply</b><small data-i18n="bot_status">Respondo tus dudas</small></div><button class="bx" onclick="toggleBot(false)"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg></button></div>
  <div class="bot-msgs" id="botMsgs"></div>
  <div class="bot-sugg" id="botSugg"></div>
  <div class="bot-input"><input id="botInput" type="text" data-i18n-ph="bot_ph" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')botSend()" /><button onclick="botSend()"><svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 2L11 13M22 2l-7 20-4-9-9-4z"/></svg></button></div>
  <div class="bot-note"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg><span data-i18n="bot_disclaimer">La IA puede cometer errores; revisá siempre los datos. Jamás recomendamos mentir en tu CV.</span></div>
</div>

<div id="modalRoot"></div>

