  ai_disclaimer:"AI can make mistakes; always double-check the data. We never recommend lying on your CV.",
  bot_disclaimer:"AI can make mistakes; always double-check the data. We never recommend lying on your CV.",
  tools_all:"See all tools",
  lead_auto:"We find matching jobs and get every application ready with your CV.",
  ap_nofilter:"If you don't select any option, we apply no restrictions: we search broadly across every available job that fits your profile.",
  lead_matches:"We show where you stand a real chance, and why.",
  lead_adapter:"We tune your CV to the keywords of the role you pick.",
  lead_analysis:"What works, what's missing, and a polished version back.",
  lead_role:"What they'll assess and the questions waiting for you.",
