  reader_hh_d:"Scans in seconds: looking for seniority and fit with their client.",
  reader_hr_d:"Checks the posting's requirements and unexplained gaps.",
  reader_bot_d:"Reads plain text: it chokes on columns, tables and images.",
  cv_translated:"Auto-translated",
  cv_edit_pro:"Edit by hand · PRO", cv_edit_on:"Editing on", cv_edit_off:"Turn on editing",
  cv_edit_hint_free:"Manual editing is a Pro feature. On your current plan you can still download the generated CV as PDF.",
  cv_edited:"Edited by you", cv_edit_hint:"Click any line to edit it. It exports exactly as you see it.", cv_restore:"Back to the auto draft",
  bot_thanks:"You're welcome! Anything else about MatchApply?", chat_clear:"Clear conversation",
  hero_eyebrow:"Obsessed with your search", hero_title:"Find the right job and show up prepared",
  hero_sub:"MatchApply finds the roles you actually fit, tailors your CV to each search and, with one click, prepares and sends all your applications.",
  hero_start:"Get started", hero_more:"Learn more ›",
  feat_title:"How does MatchApply work?", feat_intro:"Tools to stop sending the same CV everywhere and start applying with focus.",
  f1_h:"Smart match", f1_p:"A 0–100 score comparing your profile to each posting, with concrete reasons.",
  f2_h:"Tailored CV", f2_p:"We adapt your résumé to the keywords each search needs, without touching your base version.",
  f3_h:"Interview-ready", f3_p:"What's valued in each role, what to strengthen and the most likely questions. You walk in knowing.",
  cta_h:"Start today.", cta_p:"Set up your profile once and let the tools do the heavy lifting.", cta_btn:"Try MatchApply",
  ab_eyebrow:"Who are we?", ab_title:"We believe job hunting can be different.",
  ab_p1:"MatchApply was born from a simple conviction: a job seeker's time matters, and today it's wasted. Every opening gets hundreds of applications, and most people end up sending the same résumé everywhere, without knowing where they really stand a chance.",
  ab_p2:"We set out to change that with concrete tools: a score that compares your profile to each posting, an assistant that tailors your CV to what each search asks for, and a guide that prepares you for the interview. All from a profile you fill in just once.",
  ab_quote_txt:"“Applying should cost you time in interviews, not in forms.”", ab_quote_by:"Our premise",
  ab_p3:"We're obsessed with one thing: making applying feel different. Every detail — the score that tells you where you stand a chance, the CV that tailors itself, the prep before the interview — exists so you get further with less wear and tear. The experience should match the job you're after.",
  val1_h:"Your time matters", val1_p:"Every minute you don't lose to a form is a minute you spend getting ready.",
  val2_h:"Judgment, not volume", val2_p:"It's not about applying to everything, but applying well.",
  ab_cta_p:"It's all waiting for you on the other side.",
  val3_h:"A premium experience", val3_p:"Professional-grade tools so every application of yours plays in the top league.", ab_btn:"Try the tools",
  tools_h:"Your tools", tools_p:"Set up your profile once and use it everywhere. You pick where to start.",
  tab_auto:"Auto-apply", tab_matches:"Jobs", tab_adapter:"Tailored CV", tab_analysis:"CV review", tab_role:"Interview",
  prof_label:"Your profile / base CV", prof_upload:"Upload CV (PDF/DOCX)",
  prof_ph:"Paste your profile or CV as text...",
  cv_reading:"Reading your CV…", cv_done:"CV loaded and read. Review the text and use it across the tools.", cv_err:"We couldn't read the file. Try a PDF or DOCX with selectable text.",
  chips_label:"We detected",
  ap_h:"Automatic applications", ap_p:"Tell us what you're after and we take it from there. We track down the roles that suit you and get every application ready with your CV. The last word is always yours: nothing goes out until you say so.",
  ap_mod:"Work mode", ap_remote:"Remote", ap_hybrid:"Hybrid", ap_onsite:"On-site",
  ap_jor:"Schedule", ap_full:"Full-time", ap_part:"Part-time", ap_loc:"Location or time zone",
  ap_btn:"Search & apply · 1 click", ap_note:"Uses your CV above. You can review and confirm each submission.",
