  imp_s1:"Replace tasks with achievements backed by numbers (e.g.: \"improved X by 25%\").", imp_s2:"Add a 2-line summary at the top targeted to the role you want.", imp_s3:"Include the exact keywords from the posting you apply to.",
  role_h:"Interview preparation", role_p:"Tell us the role you're going for and we'll tell you what they'll look at, what's worth strengthening and the questions you're likely to face. Fewer nerves, better answers.",
